 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-116"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> 생성자를 throw 한 <xref:System.FormatException> 다음과 같은 경우:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-116">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
