-   <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-120">`id` 하나 이상의 잘못 된 규칙 ID 문자가 포함 되어 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-120">`id` contains at least one invalid rule ID character.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-121">이러한 문자는: '?', ' \*', '+', '&#124;', ' (','), ' ^', '$', '/', ';', '.', '=', '\<', ' >', ' [', ']', ' {', '} ','\\\\',' ', '\t', '\r' 및 '\n'.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-121">These characters are: '?', '\*', '+', '&#124;', '(', '), '^', '$', '/', ';', '.', '=', '\<', '>', '[', ']', '{', '}', '\\\\', ' ', '\t', '\r', and '\n'.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-122">다음 예에서는 구문을 인식 하는 문법을 "World Cup 성공한에 국가" World Cup 했습니다 국가의 이름이 차례로 나옵니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-122">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-123">이 예에서는 만듭니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 라는 개체 `winnerRule` 식별자에 전달 `WorldCupWinner` 로 <xref:System.String>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-123">The example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object named `winnerRule` and passes in the identifier  `WorldCupWinner` as a <xref:System.String>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-124"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체의 배열에 새로운 이루어져 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> 규칙에서 인식할 수에 대 한 대안을 포함 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-124">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object consists of an array of new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects containing alternatives to be recognized by the rule.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```

  
  
