 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-153"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체에 포함 될 수도 있습니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> 규칙에 의미 체계 값 및 의미 체계 키를 추가 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-153">An <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object may also contain <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> objects that add semantic values and semantic keys to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-154">음성 인식 엔진은 구가 있을 때 의미 체계 정보 뿐만 아니라 인식된 된 구와 돌아옵니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-154">The speech recognition engine will return the semantic information, as well as the recognized phrase, when it recognizes the phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-155">참조 [의미 해석 태그](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2e115391-73b3-4666-8fd1-540c529de3b0) 자세한 정보에 대 한 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-155">See [Semantic Interpretation Markup](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2e115391-73b3-4666-8fd1-540c529de3b0) for more information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-156">다음 예에서는 구문을 인식 하는 문법을 "World Cup 성공한에 국가" World Cup 했습니다 국가의 이름이 차례로 나옵니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-156">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-157">만든 후의 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체 `winnerRule` 문자열 식별자를 제공 하 고 `WorldCupWinner`, 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> 메서드를 추가 하는 문자열 "World Cup 성공한에 국가" 규칙에 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-157">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-158">예제에서는 두 개의 추가 규칙을 만든 후 `ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-158">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-159">사용 하 여 다시는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> 메서드,이 예제에서는 추가 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체를 `WorldCupWinner` 에 규칙 참조를 포함 하는 규칙 `ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-159">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-186">범위에 대 한 기본값은 `Private`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-186">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-187">만 개인 규칙을 포함 하는 문법에 루트 규칙이 또는 루트 규칙에서 참조 되는 다른 규칙에서 규칙 참조에 의해 인식에 활성화할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-187">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-188">개인 규칙 개인 규칙은 해당 포함 된 문법의 루트 규칙이로 선언 되지 않은 외부 문법에서 참조할 수 없습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-188">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-189">해당 범위로 설정 되어 있으면 `Public`, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체에서 참조에 의해 인식에 활성화 될 수는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> 포함 문법 또는 외부 문법의 규칙에서 개체로 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-189">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-190">다음 예에서는 구문을 인식 하는 문법을 "World Cup 성공한에 국가" World Cup 했습니다 국가의 이름이 차례로 나옵니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-190">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-191">라는 공용 규칙 만들 `WorldCupWinner` Public에 해당 규칙의 범위를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-191">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner` and sets the scope of that rule to Public.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope)), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica)})));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="73b9c-192">생성된 된 문법 형식은 다음과 같습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="73b9c-192">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England< /item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```
